headline: Nasdaq CEO Adena Friedman on 2026 outlook, impact of AI and IPO pipeline
summary: Nasdaq CEO and chair Adena Friedman joins 'Squawk Box' to discuss the 2026 market outlook, impact of AI, IPO pipeline, CEO sentiment, and more.

headline: 1 Reason NDAQ is Risky and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Nasdaq trades at $101.49 per share and has stayed right on track with the overall market, gaining 13.7% over the last six months. At the same time, the S&P 500 has returned 10%.
